		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />No one can answer why. Here's the code:
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.gamefaqs.com/snes/588701-street-fighter-ii-turbo/cheats">http://www.gamefaqs.com/snes/588701-str ... rbo/cheats</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />Mega Turbo	After the Capcom logo disappears on the opening credits, press Down, R, Up, L, Y, B on controller 2
<br />
<br />To make it easier, use PAR code 7E1C8814. This will make Turbo Mode have 10 Stars. Beware you can't have any more than 10, the game will crash. As you can see, it's SNES and it moves really really fast. Too fast for me to enjoy.

		

